 “Palworld”开发商在新的问答中谈论“RimWorld”的灵感和地图尺寸https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-developer-talks-rimworld-inspiration-and-map-size-in-new-qa-3492231?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=palworld-developer-会谈-边缘世界-灵感-和-新-QA中的地图大小Imogen DonovanFri, 01 Sep 2023 13:59:37 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3492231 <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p> 5月份粉丝们提出了一千多个问题</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-developer-talks-rimworld-inspiration-and-map-size-in-new-qa-3492231">《Palworld》开发者在新问答中谈论《RimWorld》的灵感和地图尺寸的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/palworld"><em>Palworld</em></a>是即将推出的开放世界生存游戏，玩家的任务是奴役可爱的生物，其开发商在新的问答中分享了其最大的灵感来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/rimworld"><em>RimWorld</em></a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/palworld-a-tale-of-adorable-monsters-friends-late-stage-capitalism-labour-exploitation-2985030">Pocketpair Inc 的首席执行官：“我们不希望‘Palworld’变得美丽和完美。我们希望注入更黑暗主题的元素，包括剥削和暴力”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/pocketpair-inc">Pocketpair Inc</a>筛选了 5 月底<em>Palworld</em>粉丝提出的一千多个问题，首席执行官 Takuro Mizobe 和多位开发者 Hawkward 涵盖了开发挑战、游戏内经济、配乐和发布后的额外内容。 </p><p><iframe title="帕尔新闻|帕尔世界是什么……？ |问答 |口袋对" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WeDZQ5SMdew?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>说到游戏世界的大小，大约有16平方公里，与<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/kingdom-come-deliverance">《天国：拯救</a>》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/metal-gear-solid-5">《合金装备5》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/state-of-decay"><em>《腐烂国度》</em></a>相当。</p><p> Mizobe承认，虽然它的规模远不如<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-legend-of-zelda-tears-of-the-kingdom"><em>《塞尔达传说：王国之泪》</em></a> ，但它与“最近发布的其他开放世界游戏”不相上下。此外，玩家在地图上移动的速度也会使其“感觉不同”。</p><p> Mizobe 透露，协调<em>Palworld</em>艺术风格的卡通元素和现实元素是一项很难解决的挑战。切换到虚幻引擎 5 使团队能够使用其高度真实的技术，同时保持更多的风格化。</p><p>但是，在谈到游戏的设计目标时，首席执行官表示， <em>Palworld</em>与<em>RimWorld</em>有很多相似之处。 “我们开始思考‘如何让<em>RimWorld</em>的殖民地模拟在 3D 世界中变得更有趣一点？’”他解释道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3492258" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3492258" style="width: 1252px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3492258" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-2.jpg" alt="" width="1252" height="795" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-2.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3492258" class="wp-caption-text"> “Palworld” 图片来源：Pocketpair Inc</figcaption></figure><p> “我们提出了将[第三人称射击]元素、殖民地模拟元素和救生艇元素结合起来的想法，但如何才能将它们很好地结合起来呢？”他继续。 “这是那里最大的挑战。”</p><p> <em>Palworld</em>计划于 2024 年 1 月在 Steam 上发布抢先体验版。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，一位前<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-v-skyrim">《上古卷轴 5：天际》</a></em>作家，现在正在学习成为一名耶稣会牧师，为<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>Starfield</em></a>虚构的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/skyrim-writer-now-priest-in-training-helped-create-religions-in-starfield-3492101">宇宙圣所宗教</a>的创建做出了贡献。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-developer-talks-rimworld-inspiration-and-map-size-in-new-qa-3492231">《Palworld》开发者在新问答中谈论《RimWorld》的灵感和地图尺寸的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
