loads/2022/07/mercury-prize-2021@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/mercury-prize-2021@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/mercury-prize-2021@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/mercury-prize-2021@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/mercury-prize-2021@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3277017" class="wp-caption-text">令人垂涎的 2021 年水星奖奖杯。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>今年的水星奖颁奖典礼将由 DJ 兼电视节目主持人 Lauren Laverne 主持。</p><p> 2022 年，Little Simz 凭借专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/little-simz-sometimes-i-might-be-introvert-review-3035754">《Sometimes I Might Be Introvert》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-wins-the-2022-mercury-prize-for-sometimes-i-might-be-introvert-3331258">获得水星奖</a>。去年十月，这位伦敦说唱歌手击败了其他最受欢迎的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/self-esteem">《自尊》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">《湿腿》</a>的竞争。</p><p>接受奖杯时，她说：“哇，我非常非常不知所措。我非常感恩，荣耀归于神。上帝非常感谢你。”</p><p>她还向制作她专辑的制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/inflo">Inflo</a>表示敬意，并表示有时在录音室“我不知道我是否能完成这张唱片。我感受到了所有的情绪并真正经历了它，他一直支持我并推动我为你们交付这张专辑。”</p><p>该活动原定于去年九月举行，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2022-ceremony-postponed-following-death-of-queen-elizabeth-ii-3306817">仪式在女王去世后的第二天晚上被取消</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.eventim.co.uk/event/the-2023-mercury-prize-eventim-apollo-17380512/?affiliate=HAL" target="_blank" rel="noopener">今年电视转播决赛的门票可在此处购买。</a></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2023-performers-announced-3492232">公布的 2023 年水星奖获奖者</a>名单首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
